# VIM MODE: Learn Programming in Neovim

Welcome to **VIM MODE**, a professional learning experience designed for developers who want to master programming AND master Vim simultaneously.

> **Why Vim?** Because the skills you learn in Vim will stay with you forever, across every system, every codebase, and every decade of your career.

---

## What is VIM MODE?

VIM MODE teaches you to learn lessons and code simultaneously in Neovim:

```
NEOVIM (Your Learning Environment)


 Lesson Text               Code Editor
 (Read-only)              (Your coding)

 - Navigation              - Live editing
 - Concepts                - Testing
 - Guidelines              - Compilation

 (Vim Keys)                (Vim Keys)


 Terminal Output (Compilation/Results)
```

### Core Workflow

1. **Read** the lesson (left buffer)
2. **Code** your solution (right buffer)
3. **Compile** from the terminal (bottom)
4. **Learn** Vim keybindings naturally through use

