## The Five Learning Stages

Each stage has 7 progressive lessons (35 lessons per language).

**Stage 1: Copying Code** - Learn by copying and understanding existing code

**Stage 2: Pseudocode to Code** - Translate English-like instructions into programs

**Stage 3: Problem to Pseudocode** - Analyze problems and write your own solutions

**Stage 4: Full Problem Solving** - Complete independence with real-world problems

**Stage 5: Capstone Projects** - Build professional-quality applications for your portfolio

