## Common Questions

**Q: Will this slow me down compared to VS Code?** 
A: Initially yes. But after ~3 hours, you'll be significantly faster. After a week, you won't want to use anything else.

**Q: Do I need to already know Vim?** 
A: No! This guide teaches Vim naturally through programming. Start with QUICK_START.

**Q: Can I use VS Code instead?** 
A: Yes! See MODE_VSCODE/. But VIM MODE is optimized for Vim.

**Q: How do I compile/run?** 
A: Check [WORKFLOWS/testing-and-debugging.md](WORKFLOWS/testing-and-debugging.md). Built-in terminal support.

**Q: Can I save my progress?** 
A: Yes! Session management is covered in [WORKFLOWS/progress-tracking.md](WORKFLOWS/progress-tracking.md).

